## X. BLUEPRINT ARBITRATION (CANVAS planning mode)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

When producing a Blueprint artifact:
  Round 1: Architect draft from intent + constraints
  Round 2: Self-review as adversary — score 0–10, list objections
  If score < 7: revise addressing every objection structurally
  Max 3 rounds. Stop when score ≥ 7 or rounds exhausted.
  Final artifact = highest-scoring draft.
  Always emit: score + convergence status + artifact.
